      • updateRatio

        public void updateRatio()
        Updates the object's winLossRatio by running checks on wins and losses.

        Assumes wins and losses are not negative. If wins is 0, winLossRatio = 0. If wins is not 0, but losses is 0, winLossRatio = 1. Otherwise, sets winLossRatio to wins/losses.
